manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: The Best Air Fryer Accessories for Dual Basket Air Fryers! The air fryer stainless steel rack, reusable liners and air fryer recipe book are the ideal accessories for dual basket air fryers, such as the Ninja DZ201 and DZ401 which have a 2-basket system. Infraovens is not associated with nor endorsed by Ninja.

Accessories for a better air frying experience EASY TO CLEAN The wide spaces in the air fryer rack makes it easy to clean, unlike other mesh-type racks that gather residue. Our rack is made with stainless steel that won't rust, peel or flake, allowing you to cook to your heart's desire knowing that it is always safe to use and easy to reuse! AVOID MESSY, STICKY AND DIFFICULT TO CLEAN RACKS Replace your mesh-style racks and opt for a wide grate air fryer rack instead, then, pair it with the air fryer mesh mat and give yourself the ease of use that you need. This air fryer accessories combo will majorly improve your air fryer game and allow you to save time, making your life easier!

PROTECT YOUR RACKS AND BASKETS Use the air fryer rectangular reusable liner to protect your air fryer rack or air fryer basket. It's also ideal to cook more liquid or more sticky types of food and it's dishwasher safe. COOK AND DEHYDRATE WITHOUT THE MESS Use the air fryer mesh mat to create a dehydrating rack that will not gather sticky, messy food residue. When finished, you can simply put it in the dishwasher.

ALLOW AIR TO CIRCULATE THROUGHOUT The dual air fryer perforated mat helps keep your baskets, air fryer trays and racks clean while still allowing air to circulate throughout, allowing food to cook more evenly and easily. MORE OPTIONS, MORE VERSATILITY The double basket air fryer stainless steel rack helps elevate food, while giving you the versatility to cook different types of recipes that otherwise wouldn't be possible.

See what's included in your Air Fryer Accessories Bundle: This air fryer accessories bundle includes: 1 x air fryer stainless steel rack, 1 x air fryer reusable liner, 1 x air fryer mesh liner, 1 x air fryer perforated liner, 1 x air fryer recipe booklet. It's compatible with the Ninja Dual Basket, 2-Basket or Double Basket Dual Zone Air Fryer.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My air fryer isn't a Ninja, but it works anyway
reviews.reviewText: It works because mine is shaped like the Ninja. I like having these so I don't have to clean my air fryer as much: I can just clean the reusable liners, which clean up easily. I also use the little rack when I am frying two things at once. One item goes directly onto my rack and the other goes onto the little one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Neat Little Additions
reviews.reviewText: We have an airfryer that you can use on one side, the other, or with a big zone in the middle. Because there's so much room, these accessories really come in handy. If I want to brush a sauce onto something or make something that might fall through the openings, these absolutely save the day!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fit as expected
reviews.reviewText: A good value and it fit as expected. There are a few recipes in the book to get you started. In the book were also explanations for each piece that came with the kit. This was helpful.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great accessories for Ninja Air fryer!
reviews.reviewText: The Accessories for Ninja Air Fryer, including the reusable sheets, liners, and rack, have enhanced my air frying experience by offering practical solutions for cooking and cleanup. The reusable sheets and liners make cleaning a breeze, providing a non-stick surface that prevents food residue from sticking to the air fryer basket. The additional rack increases the cooking capacity, allowing for more versatile meal preparation. These accessories have proven to be durable and efficient, simplifying the cooking process and making my Ninja Air Fryer even more versatile in the kitchen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This set solves a couple of problems I have with this fryer. The inserts are a real pain to clean since food sticks to every nook and cranny. You really have to scrub to get it all out. The mats, being flexible, are so much easier to clean.The other problem is that I didn't feel like enough air got underneath the food with some items and the grill rack will make a huge difference in the food I want to be crispy and not merely cooked.This came with a code for membership on their website,. so I signed up for it. Has lots of recipes and even product testing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These fit the Foodi perfectly
reviews.reviewText: These fit our Ninja Foodi 7 quart perfectly. They are easy to clean, and the metal rack, especially, gives excellent room for airflow.No real complaints, other than I would have preferred silicone inserts over fiberglass.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A good inexpensive set of accessories
reviews.reviewText: I got this for my mom who has the Ninja 2 sided air fryer. She uses it almost daily. We tried the rack with some frozen hash brown patties she loves to air fry and it took away the need to flip the patties. They were centrally heated and perfectly crisp on the outside! Yum! This was just one instance of many ideas we discussed. The mats may or may not be as useful, but time will tell.
